'''福井盗龙'''（[[属名|属名]]：''Fukuiraptor''，意为“[[福井县|福井县]]的盗贼”）是生存于现在[[日本|日本]]的一属[[白垩纪|早白垩世]]（[[巴列姆阶|巴列姆阶]]或[[阿普第阶|阿普第阶]]）中型[[大盗龙类|大盗龙类]][[兽脚亚目|兽脚亚目]]恐龙，<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Azuma|first1=Yoichi|last2=Philip J.|first2=Currie|date=2000|title=A new carnosaur (Dinosauria: Theropoda) from the Lower Cretaceous of Japan|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_canadian-journal-of-earth-sciences_2000-12_37_12/page/1735|journal=Canadian Journal of Earth Sciences|volume=37|issue=12|pages=1735–1753|doi=10.1139/e00-064|bibcode=2000CaJES..37.1735A}}</ref>所知来自于{{link-en|北谷组|Kitadani Formation}}，<ref name="CurrieAzuma-2006" />也可能是{{link-en|濑林组|Sebayashi Formation}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A tooth of Fukuiraptor aff. F. kitadaniensis from the Lower Cretaceous Sebayashi Formation, Sanchu Cretaceous, Japan: 東京学芸大学リポジトリ|url=http://ir.u-gakugei.ac.jp/handle/2309/107121|access-date=2020-10-09|website=ir.u-gakugei.ac.jp|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109051048/http://ir.u-gakugei.ac.jp/handle/2309/107121|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 叙述 ==
[[File:フクイラプトルの全身骨格化石.jpg|thumb]] 
[[正模标本|正模标本]]是一具在福井县[[胜山市|胜山市]]附近{{link-en|北谷采石场|Kitadani Formation}}（Kitadani Quarry）中发现的部分骨骼（编号为'''FPDM-V97122'''）。该标本被认为生前测量长度约为4.2米、重175千克且未发育成熟，而成年恐龙将会更大。在采石场还发现了许多其他个体的遗骸以及大量归类于该物种的肱骨、股骨和牙齿。<ref name="CurrieAzuma-2006">{{Cite journal |last1=Currie |first1=P.J. |last2=Azuma |first2=Y. |year=2006 |title=New specimens, including a growth series, of ''Fukuiraptor'' (Dinosauria, Theropoda) from the Lower Cretaceous Kitadani Quarry of Japan |journal=J. Paleont. Soc. Korea |volume=22 |issue=1 |pages=173–193 |via=ResearchGate|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40664042}}</ref>然而，同一地点发现的其他个体大多是小于正模标本个体的幼体（柯里＆东洋一，2006），最小的不到正模标本体型的四分之一。在{{link-en|濑林组|Sebayashi Formation}}的[[砾岩|砾岩]] 中发现的一颗牙齿（NDC-P0001）也被归类于福井盗龙。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Molnar|first1=Ralph E.|last2=Obata|first2=Ikuwo|last3=Tanimoto|first3=Masahiro|last4=Matsukawa|first4=Masaki|date=2009|title=A tooth of Fukuiraptor aff. F. kitadaniensis from the Lower Cretaceous Sebayashi Formation, Sanchu Cretaceous, Japan|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/43696092|journal=Bulletin of Tokyo Gakugei University, Division of Natural Sciences|volume=61|pages=105–117|via=ResearchGate}}</ref>2010年，{{link-en|格雷戈里·S·保罗|Gregory S. Paul}} 给出的尺寸为5米（16英尺）长、300千克（660磅）重。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Paul|first=Gregory S.|title=The Princeton Field Guide to Dinosaurs|url=https://archive.org/details/princetonfieldgu00paul|publisher=Princeton University Press|year=2010|location=New Jersey|pages=[https://archive.org/details/princetonfieldgu00paul/page/n98 98]}}</ref>Molina-Pérez和Larramendi在2016年估计其尺寸为4.3米（14.1英尺）长、590千克（1300磅）重。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Molina-Pérez & Larramendi|title=Récords y curiosidades de los dinosaurios Terópodos y otros dinosauromorfos|publisher=Larousse|year=2016|location=Barcelona, Spain|pages=263}}</ref>

福井盗龙与众不同的牙齿显示出与[[鲨齿龙科|鲨齿龙科]] （非常扁平，形如刀片并具有褶皱的珐琅质）和[[暴龙科|暴龙科]]（锯齿附近有倾斜的血槽）的相似性。<ref name="CurrieAzuma-2006" />正模标本还具有非常大且扁平的手爪，为最初分类于驰龙科（因为手爪被误认为是脚爪）以及现在被分类于大盗龙类起到作用。<ref name="Benson-etal-2010">{{Cite journal|last1=Benson|first1=R. B. J.|last2=Carrano|first2=M. T.|last3=Brusatte|first3=S. L.|date=2010|title=A new clade of archaic large-bodied predatory dinosaurs (Theropoda: Allosauroidea) that survived to the latest Mesozoic|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/272152523|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=97|issue=1|pages=71–78|bibcode=2010NW.....97...71B|doi=10.1007/s00114-009-0614-x|pmid=19826771|s2cid=22646156}}</ref>

== 分类 ==
最初被发现时，它被认为是[[驰龙科|驰龙科]]的一员，其叙述者认为它是与[[异特龙|异特龙]]有关的[[肉食龙类|肉食龙类]]。近期研究认为它是一种[[大盗龙类|大盗龙类]]――一个神秘的分类群，可能是[[新猎龙科|新猎龙科]]的一部分。<ref name="Benson-etal-2010" />然而，最期另一项分析表明所有大盗龙类实际上都是[[暴龙超科|暴龙超科]]，这将该属重新分类为一种[[暴龙超科|暴龙超科]]的[[虚骨龙类|虚骨龙类]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Novas |first1=F. E. |last2=Agnolín |first2=F. L. |last3=Ezcurra |first3=M. D. |last4=Canale |first4=J. I. |last5=Porfiri |first5=J. D. |year=2012 |title=Megaraptorans as members of an unexpected evolutionary radiation of tyrant-reptiles in Gondwana |url=http://www.ameghiniana.org.ar/index.php/ameghiniana/article/view/868/1618 |journal=[[Ameghiniana|Ameghiniana]] |volume=49 |issue=4(R): Suplemento Resúmenes [Abstracts] |pages=R33 |access-date=2021-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311112309/http://www.ameghiniana.org.ar/index.php/ameghiniana/article/view/868/1618 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最近对兽脚类[[瓜利乔龙|瓜利乔龙]]进行的系统发育分析表明，福井盗龙和其它大盗龙类要么是[[异特龙超科|异特龙超科]]，要么是非暴龙超科的基底虚骨龙类。<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Apesteguía |first1=Sebastián |last2=Smith |first2=Nathan D. |last3=Valieri |first3=Rubén Juárez |last4=Makovicky |first4=Peter J. |date=13 July 2016 |title=An Unusual New Theropod with a Didactyl Manus from the Upper Cretaceous of Patagonia, Argentina |journal=PLOS ONE |volume=11 |issue=7 |pages=e0157793 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0157793 |pmid=27410683 |issn=1932-6203|bibcode=2016PLoSO..1157793A |pmc=4943716 }}</ref>

